<section id="how-it-works" class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-zinc-100/35">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">Why Heftydev</h2>

        <div class="mt-8 flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-200 to-gray-300 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-500">TN</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              I&rsquo;m Trevor, a senior Rails engineer focused on complex, multi-tenant SaaS in
              regulated industries. I&rsquo;ve built production systems handling private equity fund
              administration, venture capital legal workflows, insurance operations, and
              financial compliance&mdash;all on clean, idiomatic Rails.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              I build vanilla Rails applications with consistent conventions so any Rails team
              can scale it later. No proprietary frameworks, no clever abstractions that only
              I understand.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Prototype speed, production discipline. Idiomatic Rails, customized like it&rsquo;s bespoke.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200">
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Engineer, expert network on call</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            I&rsquo;m the engineer you work with day-to-day. When needed, I pull in specialists&mdash;design,
            security review, deep domain experts&mdash;so you get senior-level depth without building
            a big agency team.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-500">Happy to sign an NDA.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-0">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-8">How I Work</h3>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-sm shrink-0">1</div>
              <div class="w-px h-full bg-gray-200 mt-2"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="pb-8">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Discovery</h4>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                We decide what <em class="not-italic font-medium text-gray-800">must</em> exist in the MVP to validate demand and pricing&mdash;then we cut everything else.
                Clarify workflows and acceptance criteria, domain constraints, compliance needs, and user expectations.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-sm shrink-0">2</div>
              <div class="w-px h-full bg-gray-200 mt-2"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="pb-8">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Prototype</h4>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Ship vertical slices fast: auth, billing, tenancy, notifications&mdash;so you demo a real product, not a mock. AI-accelerated delivery where it helps, with senior review on the critical path.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-sm shrink-0">3</div>
              <div class="w-px h-full bg-gray-200 mt-2"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="pb-8">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Harden</h4>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Turn fast output into robust software: tests where it matters, security review, tenancy boundaries, and decisions documented. AI can write code quickly; a senior engineer makes it correct.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-sm shrink-0">4</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Handoff</h4>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Your team inherits vanilla Rails conventions and a codebase structured for long-term change. Handoff-ready patterns without a bespoke framework.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
          <%= link_to "Book an MVP call", "#contact", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
